Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去  去練習樂隊曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.28,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(340.909,968.182)\1cBEFFFE\3c582738\bord8.18182}魔法展現的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  艾麗你幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九條月夜  2年級A班  天文部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那天晚上  我攻略了月夜  趕走驅魂拯救了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時理所當然地認為她那些記憶已經消失的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後就再沒有接觸過她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…已經不想再看見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而月夜還有著關於我的記憶  並且在生我的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月夜體內有女神的幾率很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還不來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經超過預定的時間1個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露娜  你沒被淋濕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等你  想跟你一起回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是搭公車上學的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻煩的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跟我上車  你這變態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須把落下的彌補回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘客  要發車了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要解決和嘉音的誤會很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在我還想維持著這狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三角關係在遊戲裡是常套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用簡單的方法來維持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,構成三角形的三個F
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稱它作戀愛ΔForce
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要立即
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Follow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟嘉音的流言  我也不清楚怎麼來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你不要纏著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Foolish
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要表現出男人的愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  我的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後
