Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不完整的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不給出結論
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜時間太短了  這樣的話好感度就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貼上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是星期天  你會去天文部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是晚上天晴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  允許入場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗  你挺上手了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有模有樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就練到這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是白亞傳來的警告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習要結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我再撐一會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼各位女士  我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是女士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  結走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要把剩下的這兩人留下來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我們聊聊天再走好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來艾麗  你不是有事要跟我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天桂木打電話跟我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木打電話給你？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢  你有什麼事找我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才第一個人就這模樣  剩下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  不好  她要走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算撞上車也要阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這老天太不配合了  不管嘉音死活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等你  想跟你一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊桂木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學事件可是提升好感度的重要機會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}雨  停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可為什麼連京也跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\an8\fs49.0909\1cF8C9F7\3c9D4536}那  那個  一起回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學必須要兩人獨處才有意義  在遊戲裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,450)\an8\fs49.0909\1cF8C9F7\3c9D4536}不…不行嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有妹妹和青梅竹馬才能插入  在遊戲裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無視京強行攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美  之前的考試考得怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照你平常…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過桂木  你要是跟我們一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕嘉音吃醋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  沒想到桂木竟然在和嘉音交往
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什麼時候的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想知道好想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了京大姐  請你放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好感度在不斷下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修復
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不過是個謠言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞和千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼她們會在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我好想吃這裡的鯛魚燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}喂  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去嘛進去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先到往常去的樂器店好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就上二樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木你吃小倉餡的可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很熱  我給你多包一層紙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在對我這般親切也晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你被驅魂附身我也不會救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了再去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為千尋說想看看樂器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都給我自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我盡好本分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道這次攻略的重要性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在跟誰說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  你有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我才沒有閒情陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以請你不要纏著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今以後我也會一直纏著你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎麼說  我都不會罷休的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美  你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾  艾麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙  好燙好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗上好久廁所了啊  肚子不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木？你在幹嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千尋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希托我幫她買貝斯的弦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不知道要買哪種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有急事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗細不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說為什麼吉他要有這麼多種類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不都是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  全都不一樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡不一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我也只是個初學者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學吉他也才半年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好棒的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼鬼價格啊  能買多少遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木  來我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人多害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣  果然還是貴的音質比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也沒搞懂  太緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才哼的是誰的歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那首啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢  算是我的歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來我們打算在舞高祭上唱原創曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過到現在也只作了個開頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還算是首挺好聽的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在構思  還不知道是不是好聽的歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要和你說這事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美和千尋都勉強進行下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥的鯛魚燒的錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個是栞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圖書館已經關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說關得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經是炮彈的光粒化為壓縮光束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到行星爆炸的光芒照亮了宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙歷20DA年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠古行星戰爭已經進行600年了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫西蒙妮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙妮·艾斯利比洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能成為夢寐以求的星團記者  簡直跟夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科學幻想類…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還是行星戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點不著邊際
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主編
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們要做的是要譴責戰爭的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫什麼宇宙餃子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被炒魷魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為懲罰要每天整理新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本去不了宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到什麼就說出口  是我的壞習慣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能變得沉默一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說很難啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  寫得和作者性格完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在圖書館和一個不可思議的男生相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生叫卡西拉吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮埃爾·卡西拉吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書是好東西喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人類驚人的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,書什麼的只是上世紀的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西拉吉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在書上亂塗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在糾正上面的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺我總在和你說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們關係變好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙妮  你簡直就像故事裡的主角一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:15:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那麼說我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角色雖然反了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和我的攻略一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那栞她還記得攻略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕從宇宙出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你勇氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和我的攻略一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題是這之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  什麼也沒寫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西拉吉掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西拉吉在戰場上被打成馬蜂窩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人舉辦了卡西拉吉的宇宙葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西拉吉  為什麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡一點悲傷都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然被粗暴地派便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是因為我和嘉音傳言的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂看…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來當不了西蒙妮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後我加了幾筆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾天後  時間膠囊回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了這宇宙防彈衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我毫髮無傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別自說自話復活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂寫設定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西拉吉被猛獸雷巴多斯活活吞噬而死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點也不心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西拉吉沒有被消化  成功脫出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直跟奇跡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要復活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點也不想見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且卡西拉吉是很沉默的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,採訪…星雲合成小蔥拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.77,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54.5455}別生氣  西蒙妮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能和你一起去採訪星雲拉麵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.50,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54.5455\fad(0,200)}待續
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這回就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是星雲…合成小蔥拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事還能寫下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是目的是一起放學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天上看著  栞出來了就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會裝作偶然碰見一樣會合的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}…不在裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}到底去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼在這裡  你不是坐車回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和你一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在車上看見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有點危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓柔弱的男生一個人回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下等下  那是男生的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是後面一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擅自觸發情節
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\pos(559.091,886.364)\1c91E3FF\bord0\fs54.5455\i1}一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與其說是攻略對像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動更像是玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說我是被攻略的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩家VS玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了  讓你送我回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓男子漢的我送你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心動了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑得真讓人心動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…你對步美和千尋也同樣笑過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂木同學原來是花花公子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花花公子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你  禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新要素來得沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}根本來不及處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們的未來絕對需要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞島高中的女生校服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要幹啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然要讓桂木同學穿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明明在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但雙方都穿男裝不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我換女裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想習慣！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說我們根本沒在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫才？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你可能是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男裝和女裝這點上就根本不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有愛就能逾越
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:19:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕  快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天將直接採訪剛結束錄音的嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}傳說中的那種事這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起放學是完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60}也會提問的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進度有點慢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好感度最大時被討厭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是進展停止就是GAMEOVER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的好感度大概是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻略初期的星期天要先攻略誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  先全員掃蕩一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼諾拉在  難道嘉音的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之那傢伙很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前她可來要過我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也算是我們的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會做到那種地步的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來玩的  你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯絡一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  艾露希呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  真不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  別讓她注意到嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比我那廢柴協力者好用多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  能被諾拉大人中意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要突然就嬉皮笑臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改變主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打聽點情報出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找艾露希有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法治署傳達的新命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索在人界潛伏的天界人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我沒聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是機密情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式發令是在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天界人指的是女神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:21:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女神是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我抓驅魂就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  哪邊的傢伙都一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在去圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以後也要好好和諾拉交涉  打聽點情報出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我交涉…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一件可以證明這座城市裡有女神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.79,0:22:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音還有幾天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而女神的攻略沒有想像中順利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:50.72,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}深くて　熱い愛しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:50.72,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}這份愛  深刻而熱烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:57.73,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}会うたびに積もるの　白い羽のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:57.73,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}每次相見慢慢積累  彷如雪白的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:03.68,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何度も　すれ違っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:03.68,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無數次  與你錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:10.73,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}スキ・キライ・ダイスキ　スクランブル交差点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:10.73,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}喜歡·討厭·最喜歡  彷徨駐足十字路口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:17.22,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}朝も昼も　夜も夢の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:17.22,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不管早晨上午  還是夜晚夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:25.49,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}中でもずっと　そばにいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:25.49,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}只想一直  與你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:31.83,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}あなたを　守りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:31.83,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}願守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:38.49,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}こんな気持ち　初めての感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:38.49,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}這份情愫  初次誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:44.85,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界を　敵にしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:44.85,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}即使與世界為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:51.70,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}私だけは　味方でいたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:51.70,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我也永遠支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:54.75,edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:54.75,edcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,3,,月夜  栞  結  步美  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,3,,這座學校到處都是女神候補
